Package com.healthcare.models

Class Patient

java.lang.Object
com.healthcare.models.Patient
public class Patient extends Object
The Patient class represents a patient in a healthcare system. It stores patient details such as ID, name, billing address, phone number, nationality, and their associated insurance policies.
